{"tid":213815,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"食緊A酸","createTime":"2017-04-23T11:18:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-16T12:54:33.000Z","uid":49923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"53ebff0abc37c74ea04dfed793f84178d8b8b46e","tid":213815,"uid":49923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T11:18:13.000Z","msg":"想問下各位連巴絲，本身我就食緊A酸宜家。<br />\n都算係食咗成3個月左右，基本上面上都叫做控制到下，但d暗瘡印就....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如無意外應該仲要幾多幾個月，但問題就嚟啦，我唔知道之前d人post過食A算嘅時候係咪靜係等A酸藥，唔知有無連住其他藥嚟食(意思係話唔知道醫生會唔會除咗a酸仲有跟多幾隻藥)。<br />\n宜家我諗返起.... 醫生除咗a酸仲有俾多兩隻藥。<br />\n想知道有食緊A酸嘅連巴絲有無好似我嗰情況咁....<br />\n最怕係宜家控制到嘅唔係a酸嘅藥效，而係嗰隻抗生素，之前都好似有上網睇過a酸唔可以連埋抗生素食，但唔知點解呢個醫生會俾埋抗生素。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/23/191624_4d84f75c6af32d36d419e217de95907b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F23%2F191624_4d84f75c6af32d36d419e217de95907b.jpg&h=bed82af2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/23/191625_4d84f75c6af32d36d419e217de95907b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F23%2F191625_4d84f75c6af32d36d419e217de95907b.jpg&h=56cfba53&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/23/191625_06a0a7c2be50ea1abe03e3d8d9f7c7b0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F23%2F191625_06a0a7c2be50ea1abe03e3d8d9f7c7b0.jpg&h=79193d29&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"53752b5bc7eb56b7912ec4aa7a367c45e2c82b43","tid":213815,"uid":5812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T11:34:35.000Z","msg":"西醫通經絡"},{"pid":"dbe9c535f528d42ec40b541eced3eaccd0cf0683","tid":213815,"uid":8584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T11:51:07.000Z","msg":"以前食過 開頭幾個月除左a酸之外 仲有加抗生素<br />\n用黎防止爆發期<br />\n印呢啲就a酸幫唔到你嫁啦<br />\n搞好左啲暗瘡先<br />\n好返哂先再搞去印啦"},{"pid":"e3367d810ce1bc453d0fbaa067c23356c282406e","tid":213815,"uid":99885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T11:59:00.000Z","msg":"食多兩三個月 睇情況有冇穩定<br />\n暗瘡印其實好易搞 有錢既去專業醫生到做激光or hifu 半年內應該搞得店 只係呢段時間要忍受下"},{"pid":"61a9ca10a45d6d237e93d6f302bf4aaaee05fe65","tid":213815,"uid":52608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T12:02:13.000Z","msg":"頭一個月有連其他藥食 好似都係消炎<br />\n之後齋食 慢慢增加劑量最多到30mg<br />\ntotal食左半年有多 <br />\n食到最後兩個月就開始一粒都唔生<br />\nd印會慢慢退<br />\n醫生話a酸除左去暗瘡都會改善皮膚 <br />\n如果再唔滿意就番去搵佢做激光"},{"pid":"3a67874a78087f5804905c2cf4ab5fb26740f0ed","tid":213815,"uid":49923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T14:04:30.000Z","msg":"睇嚟咁樣都好d，因為見到大家都話會有連多一兩隻藥，自己攞嚟擔心，因為仲諗緊a酸係咪唔可以連抗生素食呢"},{"pid":"f3a880aab16d71a24b3eaeb197189c748214c3e6","tid":213815,"uid":727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T04:46:14.000Z","msg":"食藥連診金幾錢？"},{"pid":"bead586a13ba539d77238ad5eab4ab777141e214","tid":213815,"uid":93413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T12:54:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇嚟咁樣都好d，因為見到大家都話會有連多一兩隻藥，自己攞嚟擔心，因為仲諗緊a酸係咪唔可以連抗生素食呢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但其實通常係頭一個月先會連住食，之後就齋a酸"}]}